        "action": "Repeal Pensions Schemes Act provisions on investment of private pension pots",
        "additional_details": "I believe these new powers are not in the best interests of the pension holder and could possibly yield a significantly lower return on future investments.",
        "background": "The Government recently had legislation enacted to seize powers over the investment of private pension pots. I want these powers to be abolished.",
